metadata.description:
As the astronaut moved silently through the clouds, he greeted the people he passed with a smile. Enjoying this extraordinary journey in the sky, the astronaut gave people hope. Perhaps he had been commissioned to make further discoveries deeper into the mysterious universe.

The Passenger in the Clouds kept moving forward, soaring above the clouds, taking people beyond their imagination. His journey ignited the fire of discovery in people and pushed them to new horizons to unravel the secrets of the universe.

-*Fall I Created by DRΞAMΞR*-
